---
title: Southeast Asian Pork Schnitzel with Soy-Ginger Potatoes & Apple Slaw
description: Roasted spuds are the perfect accompaniment to panko-crumbed pork and a rainbow apple slaw that'll have you experiencing a
magical fusion feast with ease. For the big finish, pull the rabbit out of the hat by topping your pork with a creamy mayo. Tada!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-southeast-asian-pork-schnitzel-8a7f8dc8.jpg
